			<div class="smallfont">1 Attachment(s)</div>
		
		
		<div>The Size of what appears on the screen is a direct result of 2 things....<br />
<br />
1. The animation file has a line that originally defines them as either 40 x 40 ...or 24 x 24...I forget which..but it describes the size of the first spell icon in the gemicons file.<br />
<br />
2. Increasing the size of the gemicons.tga files to a level that maintains the aspect ratio...in this one I increased it to 512 x 512 just for the heck of it.  <br />
<br />
I think that it must be the power of 2 rule that governs it.  But that's really all I did.  <br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
New Screenies of how it looks with both Warcraft Icons and T King icons are up...because I'm illiterate with posting they are on 2 different posts.  I'll put em up for download if you guys want em.</div>
